subject: Poker (Card Game)
Cards and Card Games
lead_paragraph: Last year’s champion, Peter Eastgate, was eliminated late Monday in 78th place, winning $68,979. Just three gold bracelet winners remained in a field of 51 players after two hours of play Tuesday.
